   condImmunities:[], senses:"Darkvision 60 ft.; Passive Perception 10",
   languages:"Primordial (Terran)",
   desc:"Gargoyles are sculptures inhabited by elemental spirits. Wings and magic allow their heavy stone bodies to fly, and they often perch where they can blend in amid ornate architecture, rock formations, or mundane statues. Most serve magic-users; if left to their own devices, they play cruel pranks and steal treasures.",
